<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fitness Tracker - FAQ</title>
    <!-- Link to the main.css file -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Dyslexic&display=swap">
</head>
<body class="<%= theme %> <%= fontPref %>">

<% if (messages.success) { %>
    <div class="flash success"><%= messages.success %></div>
<% } %>
<% if (messages.error) { %>
    <div class="flash error"><%= messages.error %></div>
<% } %>

<!-- Navbar -->
<nav>
    <div class="hamburger" onclick="toggleMenu()">
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
    </div>
    
    <ul>
        <li><a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/dashboard" class="nav-link">Dashboard</a></li>

        <!-- Fitness Dropdown Button -->
        <li class="dropdown">
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="dropbtn" onclick="toggleDropdown()">Fitness</a>
            <div class="dropdown-content">
                <a href="/workout" class="dropdown-item">Generate Workout</a>
                <a href="/water" class="dropdown-item">Water Tracker</a>
                <a href="/sleep" class="dropdown-item">Sleep Tracker</a>
            </div>
        </li>

        <li><a href="/faq" class="nav-link">FAQ and Feedback</a></li>
        <li><a href="/settings" class="nav-link">Settings</a></li>

        <!-- User Icon -->
        <% if (user) { %>
            <li class="user-icon">
                <a href="/profile">
                    <span><%= user.username %></span>
                    <img src="/<%= user.profileIcon || 'avatarblack.png' %>" alt="User Icon" />
                </a>
            </li>
        <% } else { %>
            <li><a href="/users/login" class="nav-link">Login</a></li>
            <li><a href="/users/register" class="nav-link">Sign Up</a></li>
        <% } %>
    </ul>
</nav>

    <header>
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>General Fitness Questions</h2>
            <dl>
                <dt>What is the best way to get started with a fitness routine?</dt>
                <dd>The best way to start is by setting realistic goals, choosing exercises you enjoy, and gradually increasing the intensity. It's also important to balance strength training, cardio, and flexibility exercises.</dd>
                
                <dt>How often should I work out to see results?</dt>
                <dd>For most people, working out 3-5 times a week is optimal for seeing progress, depending on the intensity and your fitness level. Consistency is key!</dd>

                <dt>Should I focus on cardio or strength training?</dt>
                <dd>A balanced approach is recommended. Cardio is great for heart health, while strength training helps build muscle and increase metabolism. A mix of both is ideal.</dd>
            </dl>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>App-Related Questions</h2>
            <dl>
                <dt>What is this fitness app all about?</dt>
                <dd>This app provides a comprehensive platform for tracking your fitness journey. It includes workout plans, progress tracking, water intake, sleep monitoring, and more—all in one place!</dd>
                
                <dt>How do I generate a workout?</dt>
                <dd>Simply go to the workout section, enter your target muscle group, preferred difficulty level, and exercise type. You can also choose to include exercise instructions for better guidance.</dd>

                <dt>Can I track my nutrition with this app?</dt>
                <dd>At the moment, the app focuses on fitness and health tracking, but nutrition tracking is something we’re working on for future updates.</dd>
            </dl>
        </section>

        <hr width="100%" size="3" noshade>

        <!-- Feedback Section -->
        <section class="feedback-section">
            <h2>Feedback</h2>
            <p>Your feedback is very important to us! Please fill out the form below if you have any suggestions, questions, or comments.</p>
            <form action="/submit-feedback" method="POST">
                <label for="feedbackName">Your Name (Optional)</label>
                <input type="text" name="name" id="feedbackName" placeholder="Enter your name">
                <br>

                <label for="feedbackEmail">Your Email (Optional)</label>
                <input type="email" name="email" id="feedbackEmail" placeholder="Enter your email">
                <br>

                <label for="feedbackMessage">Your Feedback</label>
                <textarea name="message" id="feedbackMessage" rows="5" placeholder="Enter your feedback here..." required></textarea>
                <br>

                <button type="submit">Submit Feedback</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Fitness Tracker App</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Toggle the dropdown menu visibility
        function toggleDropdown() {
            const dropdown = document.querySelector('.dropdown');
            dropdown.classList.toggle('active');
        }
        
        function toggleMenu() {
            const navList = document.querySelector('nav ul');
            navList.classList.toggle('active');
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
